parameters:
Bunny-chan: Now then, let's start the double celebration
party for the inauguration of Shark Broccoli as the new
mayor and the succession of Orca Asparagus as the great
leader❤︎ Cheers!

Memimi: Mayor Shark Broccoli... I'm so moved...! To think
this day would come... *sniff*...

Mayor Shark Broccoli: It's all thanks to you, Duke Shark...
Orca Asparagus and Drillmaid are also grateful. From now on,
I will work with them to atone for our mistakes and rebuild
the city...

Memimi: How splendid... What a noble person you are...! I
was fortunate to be picked up by Lord Shark Broccoli...

Brachiocondor: Heh heh, you drinking?! Good booze, right...?
The great leader is having orange juice though! Can't use
tax money for this, so I splurged out of my own pocket!

Memimi: Don't bother me, drunkard... I'm having a heartfelt
conversation with Lord Shark Broccoli right now... But I
must admit, the drinks are indeed delicious... Thank you...

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan, congratulations~! You've unified
all the organizations in the city, amazing~! You're
incredible, so awesome!

Memimi: Thank you, Bunny-chan... You've helped me a lot in
Monster Fight. In a way, you might be my greatest comrade in
arms...

Anomalocaris Mosman: Mos mos... You're something else, you
know... When I first met you, I thought you were just a
noisy little girl! But I admit it... You are truly worthy to
stand above all monsters as the real deal!!

Memimi: Anomalocaris Mosman... You were quite a formidable
foe too. A fine monster worthy of being my subordinate...

Cerberus Octopus: Kekeke, let's take a commemorative photo!
A picture with all the big shots of the city gathered
together, lots of folks will want it!! Wonder how much it'll
fetch?

Memimi: Cerberus Octopus, as always, you love money... Since
becoming my subordinate, it seems you've stopped your
reckless moneymaking schemes... Well, fine, let's have it
taken!
